ade487a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ade487a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol><li><b> Custom Currency Exchange Rates<\/b><b><br \/><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">SIH now allows users to set custom currency exchange rates. This feature is especially useful for traders:<\/span><\/li><\/ol><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When trading with users from other countries, adjusting the rate provides more accurate price displays.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can align the exchange rate with your region to simplify planning purchases and sales.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c5da13 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3c5da13\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/price_11zon-1024x576.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-685\" alt=\"Inventory Updates\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/price_11zon-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/price_11zon-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/price_11zon-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/price_11zon-1536x864.webp 1536w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/price_11zon-650x366.webp 650w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/price_11zon.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/